events.name: Kotlin/Everywhere GDG Morelia - Android Kotlin Fundamentals

venue.name: Instituto de Innovación Mentes en Movimiento

events.description:
Want to get started with Kotlin, but don't know where to begin? Join us for our Kotlin/Everywhere event.
Together we'll work through several Android labs. You will get hands-on experience with Kotlin in Android.

Bring a laptop (PC, Mac or Chromebook). The labs will run on all of the latest versions of the popular browsers. For the best experience, make sure your laptop has Chrome or Firefox installed. Don’t forget your charger!

group_profile.intro: Este grupo se alinea al programa GDG. Ha sido creado para generar la oportunidad de conectar con desarrolladores y personas interesadas en las tecnologías de Google y para ayudarnos entre los participantes a desarrollar habilidades técnicas.
